# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# ALFANUMRIK — Local Development Template (.env.local)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Copy this file to `.env.local`, then fill in the values you actually need.
#
#   cp .env.local.example .env.local
#
# For the FULL inventory (production, Edge Functions, optional integrations),
# see `.env.example` and `ENVIRONMENT_SETUP.md`.
#
# Rule of thumb for local dev:
#   • The 3 SUPABASE vars are mandatory — nothing starts without them.
#   • AI (ANTHROPIC, VOYAGE) is only needed if you touch /api/foxy or the
#     AI Edge Functions locally.
#   • Razorpay is only needed if you touch /api/payments/* flows.
#   • Everything else can stay unset — graceful degradation kicks in.
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════


# ─── REQUIRED (app won't boot without these) ────────────────────────────────

NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJhbGci...your-anon-key
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=eyJhbGci...your-service-role-key


# ─── Optional: AI features (skip if not working on Foxy / quiz generation) ──

# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-...
# VOYAGE_API_KEY=pa-...


# ─── Optional: Payment features (skip unless debugging /api/payments) ───────

# RAZORPAY_KEY_ID=rzp_test_xxxxxxxx
# RAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET=your-test-secret
# RAZORPAY_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_your-test-webhook


# ─── Optional: Admin panel access ──────────────────────────────────────────

# SUPER_ADMIN_SECRET=any-long-local-string


# ─── Optional: Redis (skip — in-memory fallback is fine locally) ───────────

# UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL=
# UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN=


# ─── Optional: Sentry (skip — console logging is fine locally) ─────────────

# NEXT_PUBLIC_SENTRY_DSN=


# Notes:
#   • Edge Function secrets (MAILGUN_*, SEND_EMAIL_HOOK_SECRET, ADMIN_API_KEY,
#     WHATSAPP_*, OCR_*, ENVIRONMENT, SITE_URL) DO NOT belong in this file.
#     Set them with `supabase secrets set KEY=value` or via the Supabase
#     Dashboard → Edge Functions → Secrets.
#   • Vercel-injected vars (VERCEL_*, NODE_ENV, NEXT_PHASE, CI) are set by the
#     runtime — don't set them here.
